title: FK Železničar Pančevo
text:
Fudblski klub Železničar Pančevo () is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in the city of <a href="Pan%C4%8Devo">Pančevo</a>. They currently compete in the second division <a href="Serbian%20First%20League">Serbian First League</a>.
History.
Železničar was founded in 1947. and during his history club mostly competed in lower ranks. They qualified for the <a href="Serbian%20First%20League">Serbian First League</a> for the first time in season <a href="2020%E2%80%9321%20Serbian%20First%20League">2020–21</a> after finishing first in <a href="Serbian%20League%20Vojvodina">Serbian League Vojvodina</a> in previous season.
